overview: The user wanted to significantly improve the visual appeal and overall
  aesthetic of their sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was too
  generic. The agent initiated a comprehensive review of the app's styling,
  examining global CSS, main layouts, and individual UI components. Based on
  this analysis, the agent developed and implemented a new sleep-themed design.
  This involved introducing a calming color palette, enhancing the main
  questionnaire form with subtle background elements and a more engaging
  progress indicator, and redesigning the introduction section to be more
  welcoming with feature cards. Additionally, various form fields and UI
  components like checkboxes, sliders, radio buttons, and cards were updated to
  align with the new aesthetic, resulting in a more polished, professional, and
  calming user experience tailored for a sleep health application.
